@clehene  This is a an extension of enhancement: #142 for the CLI.

Currently progress support will show up if --verbose is specified in the CLI or verbose=True is passed in to the SDK directly, however it drastically reduces overall performance for folder upload/download when there are a large number of files, due to the single threaded nature of Python and the constant context switching between the callbacks and the actual upload/download.

That being said this is something the team is aware of and is part of the current planning discussion for the upcoming milestone. @matt1883 will be able to share more details once we have them.

